p: Filed on the 21st day of Oct 1887 HM Sutton Clerk

I hereby certify that the within & foregoing recognizance was entered into and acknowledged before me, and the same is hereto certified to the Clerk of the District Court for record of accordance with the provisions of Section 1035 of the Code of Washington Territory
Witness my hand this 20th day of October AD 1887
WH Bush Sheriff of Chehalis County Washington Territory
